{"tid":388661,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"叫我個朋友唔好再錄音，佢答佢懶，應該點回好","createTime":"2017-09-05T15:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T18:49:25.000Z","uid":129039,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f221e67b936965e36184747cea733b87a0b13ef8","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"當個個都好似你咁撚得閒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為懶所以錄音，屌你普通短句&quot;好呀我地聽日一齊食囉&quot;，乃至長句&quot;我諗呢份功課呢應該xxxxxxx&quot;乜差都錄音，有冇諗過人想唔想聽、得唔得閒聽架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9165246bbdd63360774f2707d3cfa047a2dfaf1a","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed52bc6a4ef0f370ada21420ca04012609bb4fd","tid":388661,"uid":531,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"叫佢用voice input"},{"pid":"9a657856fb06fcc9d95a328004f1f53c6343e19f","tid":388661,"uid":28831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"你答返佢你懶唔撚想聽之後唔好再覆佢"},{"pid":"7bead92ccf66b7467f419beddece210c58b4ab49","tid":388661,"uid":128229,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙<br />\n單字都錄音比佢"},{"pid":"04ac5a03836ef909a19416bc8c7b75d9214e7a5c","tid":388661,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"BLOCK佢"},{"pid":"78278949dc9e880ae3e384c6b0a67db0c88e082d","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢用voice input</blockquote><br />\n之後佢會話用語音輸入仲耐過用錄音 不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfd4ecfbb4ed94f927134d3e0f3307724a7f258","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB