l/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484435cea34571e9f033d3e90a139683bd52f015","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錄返比佢 一句嘢都要拖到長一長空白勁耐</blockquote><br />\n下次佢有野問我個陣試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等佢仲錄得咁爽吖嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeffa3a9db8f7ef4b1a9498255aa344bae24efd5","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔好覆佢， 等佢問你既時候答佢。 懶得覆你～</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用錄音拖長嚟講懶得覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3425ae5817b8e331082e3fa20c0a7483d76ff8","tid":388661,"uid":15698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你聽"},{"pid":"f75738e0d36a3b9a9ae57075627dcc92e18ef03a","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長嘅分幾兩分鐘就算啦，得嗰幾秒嗰啲真係心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果真係又長又難用文字表達都算<br />\n有啲好似唱歌咁 講兩隻字又停一下 冇啦啦又errrr幾秒 仲有有一半係廢話 好似嗰啲聆聽考試咁 成段錄音得一兩句係有用 但係你唔聽晒又可以會get錯/漏 如果想重複多次又要聽番成段<br />\n真係把鬼火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4353e8cab45b3ce0c5a2c8d406b43eb7b8f8f894","tid":388661,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人叫你聽</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你睇我個po添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f977a138ee28b3f6847330931f838f109daaee1","tid":388661,"uid":15698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇人叫你聽</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你睇我個po添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住 我走"},{"pid":"0871578a5ab9c171c4c3dbec9fc763ab426bcc2a","tid":388661,"uid":48285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"每個訊息都錄片俾佢"},{"pid":"a2975766f04e1d962187f8845c981d19d0aa78f4","tid":388661,"uid":51097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錄返比佢 一句嘢都要拖到長一長空白勁耐</blockquote><br />\n最後大叫"},{"pid":"9ae3c12767c2c05e2ed40e6c0d9958e6653cee82","tid":388661,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"忍/絕交"},{"pid":"a51db3f188b210a315e7306cbd46eb16d53d48d8","tid":388661,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"我會唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}